Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Han!\NMaster Han!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Han!\NMaster Han!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Doctor is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stall her.\NGo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go get Li!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Doctor! Li, the Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Han Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you looking to learn Kung Fu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Never too late to start,\Neven for an old woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We start with jacket on - jacket off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off jacket, put on jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he told you to stall me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I did nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He did ask, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we get tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here for tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Li?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:04:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kung Fu is very empowering--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...with all due respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I already lost one son to your "path."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not lose another.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what Li means to you,\Nbut I won't have him put in harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We both agree.\NIf you could only see how Kung Fu helps him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Each time life knocked me down, Kung Fu\Nhelped me find my way back to the proper path.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a new position at a hospital in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a chance to restart for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why two hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can give one to Li when he finds the\Ncourage to come out from behind your screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you even going to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was training, not fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NCan I have your gloves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the run up is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.10,0:23:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But the balance and the jump sells it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.75,0:23:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm going to master this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.11,0:23:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You will.\NOne day, when you need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.08,0:24:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the run up is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.05,0:31:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you, Li?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.19,0:31:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we loving New York yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.04,0:31:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,More missing Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.67,0:31:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The school misses you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.49,0:31:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.61,0:31:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.31,0:31:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shifu...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.77,0:31:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made a new friend here,\Nwho asked me to teach him Kung Fu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.05,0:31:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Kung Fu can help your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.17,0:31:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.34,0:31:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that helps others and\Nbenefits yourself is a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.42,0:35:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...but downtown price is lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.21,0:35:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.17,0:35:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay okay, take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.54,0:36:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.42,0:39:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Free pizza, freshly made.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.33,0:39:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
